<!-- Rules go here -->

## Anti-Patterns — Never Generate

- `localStorage.setItem('token', ...)` — use httpOnly cookies
- `dangerouslySetInnerHTML` without sanitization — use a sanitizer library
- `eval()`, `exec()`, `Function()` constructor — find another way
- Bare `except:` clauses in Python — always specify exception types
- `any` type in TypeScript when a real type is knowable — use `unknown` if truly dynamic
- SQL string interpolation — always use parameterized queries
- Hardcoded credentials of any kind — use env vars
- Synchronous I/O inside async functions

